    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Jaidee (spa, cc ski, casino-only upd rd prog) by: </span>
      most of the dudes in my life
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/17295672-jaidee-spa-cc-ski-casino-only-upd-rd-prog?shelf=two-stars-books">two-stars-books</a>
          </div>
